    <item>
      <title>特朗普在棕榈滩向富有的捐赠者试镜副总统候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-auditions-vp-picks-before-wealthy-donors-in-palm-beach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)借鉴了他主持真人秀节目《学徒》(The Apprentice)的经历，本周末在富有的捐助者面前展示了竞选搭档的最佳竞争者，从而加强了他对可能的竞选搭档的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-auditions-vp-picks-before-wealthy-donors-in-palm-beach</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 17:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其确认因加沙战争而停止与以色列的所有贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/turkey-halts-all-trade-with-israel-officials</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名知情官员周四早些时候表示，土耳其确认将停止与以色列的所有贸易，直到该国允许不间断且充足的人道主义援助流入加沙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/turkey-halts-all-trade-with-israel-officials</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“我们做了什么？”斯托米·丹尼尔斯律师在特朗普获胜时说道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-argues-gag-order-bars-him-from-responding-to-rude-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2016 年大选前，成人电影明星斯托米·丹尼尔斯 (Stormy Daniels) 花了 13 万美元对涉嫌与唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的婚外情保持沉默，她的代理律师在作证时表示，他担心自己可能帮助这位房地产大亨入主白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/trump-argues-gag-order-bars-him-from-responding-to-rude-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬资助竞标反对驱逐麦卡锡的立法者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ken-griffin-funds-push-against-lawmaker-behind-mccarthy-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citadel 的肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 正在出资推动击败前众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡 (Kevin McCarthy) 下台的保守派之一，以重塑分裂严重的共和党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ken-griffin-funds-push-against-lawmaker-behind-mccarthy-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方逮捕 200 人，在冲突后拆除加州大学洛杉矶分校抗议营地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前一天晚上与反抗议者发生暴力事件后，身着防暴装备的警察拆除了亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在洛杉矶加州大学搭建的路障和帐篷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓首席执行官飞往南非推动 390 亿美元收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/bhp-woos-south-africa-in-pursuit-of-39-billion-anglo-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司已向南非部署了包括首席执行官在内的高级团队，这家全球最大的矿业公司正在加大努力争取政府官员、监管机构和当地股东的支持，所有这些人都可能会决定其拟议合作的结果与竞争对手英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/bhp-woos-south-africa-in-pursuit-of-39-billion-anglo-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
